   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Text written twice, with the upper copy originally sealed);;Year 31, Hathyr 12, in Philadelpheia of the Arsinoite nome. A notification to Alexandros, chief policeman, from Antigenes, a Macedonian, of the troop of Nikanor, cleruch. I have lost a white female ass, which escaped from Nikias by night, of which the value is 80 drachmai.</ab>
